.page-header#authors
  %h3 Authors
%p
  Every map must have a list of the Minecraft users who have contributed to the map in some way. A minimum of one author is required. Each author must have their Minecraft UUID and the role they played in the creation of the map specified.

%h5.elements Author Elements
%table.table.table-striped
  %tr
    %th Element
    %th Description
    %th Value
    %th Default
  %tr
    %td
      %code uuid
    %td
      = label "Required", "danger"
      The author's Minecraft user UUID.
    %td
      = link_to "UUID", "http://mcuuid.com"
    %td
  %tr
    %td
      %code role
    %td
      = label "Required", "danger"
      A brief description of how the user contributed.
    %td
      = label "String"
    %td